errado.

90
00:10:10,340 --> 00:10:13,420
Agora, diga-me,
Dr. Schwartz...

91
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:16,140
o que acha que tem
a oferecer à Lestercorp?

92
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:19,420
